						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClassBE7854983C084619BADD3D4FDB98AFBB"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">​The Department of
Administrative Services, Procurement Services (DAS PS ) and OF (Oregon Forward)
Program is sending this notification as a courtesy to all authorized purchasers
of price agreement <a href="https&#58;//gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/external/purchaseorder/poSummary.sdo?docId%3D8275%26releaseNbr%3D0%26external%3Dtrue%26parentUrl%3Dclose&amp;data=05%7c02%7cKimberley.wisdom%40oregon.gov%7cc1658fc7536144fa370408de2863b06f%7caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7c0%7c0%7c638992605812715219%7cUnknown%7cTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7c0%7c%7c%7c&amp;sdata=8C5QY2QWDHsz5j0uKGrwifn6nJpnx34eafszjdgpf5o%3D&amp;reserved=0">8275</a>
for temporary staffing services by way of amendment 11.</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Price agreement <a href="https&#58;//gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/external/purchaseorder/poSummary.sdo?docId%3D8275%26releaseNbr%3D0%26external%3Dtrue%26parentUrl%3Dclose&amp;data=05%7c02%7cKimberley.wisdom%40oregon.gov%7cc1658fc7536144fa370408de2863b06f%7caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7c0%7c0%7c638992605812737083%7cUnknown%7cTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7c0%7c%7c%7c&amp;sdata=G2iywBRdrp7QfGe78220GRVB6rHpyIqAwYp9oQiMz7c%3D&amp;reserved=0">8275</a>
has been amended to reflect the following changes&#58;</p><ol type="1" style="direction&#58;ltr;unicode-bidi&#58;embed;margin-top&#58;0in;margin-bottom&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;"><li value="1" style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Revise some provisions of the
     agreement.</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Revise attachment A
     specifications and position descriptions.</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Revise attachment B schedule
     of prices.</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Revise attachment D ordering
     instrument contract terms and conditions.</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Revise attachment D-1 state
     agency work order contract.</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Revise attachment D-2 public
     body work order.</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Incorporate attachment D-3
     work order contract amendment state</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Incorporate attachment D-4
     work order amendment public body</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Revise attachment E volume
     sales reports (VSR) and vendor collected administrative fee (VCAF).</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Revise attachment E exhibit
     E-1 VSR spreadsheet.</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Revise attachment F contact
     information for the parties.</span></li></ol><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">You can find Price
Agreement <a href="https&#58;//gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/external/purchaseorder/poSummary.sdo?docId%3D8275%26releaseNbr%3D0%26external%3Dtrue%26parentUrl%3Dclose&amp;data=05%7c02%7cKimberley.wisdom%40oregon.gov%7cc1658fc7536144fa370408de2863b06f%7caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7c0%7c0%7c638992605812752942%7cUnknown%7cTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7c0%7c%7c%7c&amp;sdata=PCLTKRVhpvi9uAXOF9f4UncZjkb%2BpzxLZgw0QL8S9C4%3D&amp;reserved=0">8275</a>
and all amendments on OregonBuys under “Attachments”. <a href="https&#58;//gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/&amp;data=05%7c02%7cKimberley.wisdom%40oregon.gov%7cc1658fc7536144fa370408de2863b06f%7caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7c0%7c0%7c638992605812768130%7cUnknown%7cTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7c0%7c%7c%7c&amp;sdata=zU1MwnT0YEJISo1mzCZgbAYC4mRl6mULVyOtA8BzgL0%3D&amp;reserved=0">OregonBuys</a></p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">For more information
regarding this message, contact Rena Montes, Oregon Forward Program Contracts
Manager, at 503-507-1246 or via email <a href="mailto&#58;info.ofp@das.oregon.gov">info.ofp@das.oregon.gov</a>.<br></p></div>
