							<div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">[orcpplink]NASPO electronic monitoring products &amp; services - participating addendum for electronic monitoring and services with alcohol 06/30/2025</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h4><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="877396b7-418e-4c23-887f-a3bd91b1f9cd" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass76489F8E1EF34A2A836632F3B735B902"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">​DAS SPS
has executed a new Participating Addendum for Electronic Monitoring Products
and Services with Alcohol Monitoring Systems, Inc., dba SCRAM Systems.<br></p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">The
following products are available from these agreements&#58;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Radio
Frequency Monitoring (RFM)</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Alcohol
Monitoring (AM)</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">GPS
Satellite Monitoring (GPSM)</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">&#160;</p><div style="direction&#58;ltr;"><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="direction&#58;ltr;border-style&#58;solid;border-color&#58;#a3a3a3;border-width&#58;1pt;"><tbody><tr><td style="border-style&#58;solid;border-color&#58;#a3a3a3;border-width&#58;1pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.7298in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Contractor
  Name</p></td><td style="border-style&#58;solid;border-color&#58;#a3a3a3;border-width&#58;1pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;0.9763in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Contract
  Number</p></td><td style="border-style&#58;solid;border-color&#58;#a3a3a3;border-width&#58;1pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.3319in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Contact
  Information</p></td><td style="border-style&#58;solid;border-color&#58;#a3a3a3;border-width&#58;1pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.3465in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Radio
  Frequency Monitoring (“RFM”)</p></td><td style="border-style&#58;solid;border-color&#58;#a3a3a3;border-width&#58;1pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.1069in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Alcohol
  Monitoring (“AM”)</p></td><td style="border-style&#58;solid;border-color&#58;#a3a3a3;border-width&#58;1pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.1145in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">GPS
  Satellite Monitoring (“GPSM”)</p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-style&#58;solid;border-color&#58;#a3a3a3;border-width&#58;1pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.7298in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Allied
